 height="966" width="1280" aria-labelledby="fig27" loading="lazy" /><figcaption><span class="heading">Figure 27</span> Pulmonary involvement in a 72-year-old man. CT image shows honeycomb changes in the lower lobes of both lungs.<div class="core-figure-tools"><ul><li><a class="core-figure-download-powerpoint" href="/action/downloadFigures?doi=10.1148%2Frg.315105735&amp;id=fig27">Download as PowerPoint</a></li></ul></div></figcaption></figure></div><div class="figure-wrap"><figure id="fig28a" class="graphic"><img src="/cms/10.1148/rg.315105735/asset/images/105735fig28a.jpeg" height="1108" width="1280" loading="lazy" /><figcaption><span class="heading">Figure 28a</span> <!-- There is no content. --><div class="core-figure-tools"><ul><li><a class="core-figure-download-powerpoint" href="/action/downloadFigures?doi=10.1148%2Frg.315105735&amp;id=fig28a">Download as PowerPoint</a></li></ul></div></figcaption></figure></div><div class="figure-wrap"><figure id="fig28b" class="graphic"><img src="/cms/10.1148/rg.315105735/asset/images/105735fig28b.jpeg" height="1128" width="1280" loading="lazy" /><figcaption><span class="heading">Figure 28b</span> <!-- There is no content. --><div class="core-figure-tools"><ul><li><a class="core-figure-download-powerpoint" href="/action/downloadFigures?doi=10.1148%2Frg.315105735&amp;id=fig28b">Download as PowerPoint</a></li></ul></div></figcaption></figure></div><div class="figure-wrap"><figure id="fig29a" class="graphic"><img src="/cms/10.1148/rg.315105735/asset/images/105735fig29a.jpeg" height="1022" width="1280" loading="lazy" /><figcaption><span class="heading">Figure 29a</span> <!-- There is no content. --><div class="core-figure-tools"><ul><li><a class="core-figure-download-powerpoint" href="/action/downloadFigures?doi=10.1148%2Frg.315105735&amp;id=fig29a">Download as PowerPoint</a></li></ul></div></figcaption></figure></div><div class="figure-wrap"><figure id="fig29b" class="graphic"><img src="/cms/10.1148/rg.315105735/asset/images/1057